## bold
Making your texts bold is one way to highlight them.  
To bold your text, surround words with two asterisks "**".  
For example, "This is a **good** project to learn Markdown syntax."

## italics  
Making your texts in italics is another way to highlight them.  
To make your texts italic, surround words with an underscore "_".  
For example, "This is a _good_ project to learn Markdown syntax."